# CineVerse Development Roadmap

Build the application in multiple phases. Complete each phase entirely before moving to the next one. Every phase must be production-ready, tested, responsive, and follow the project's design system.

---

# Phase 1 — Project Foundation

## Objective

Set up the project architecture and development environment.

### Tasks

* Create a Next.js 15 project using the App Router.
* Configure TypeScript.
* Install Tailwind CSS.
* Configure ESLint and Prettier.
* Set up Husky and lint-staged.
* Configure environment variables.
* Create the project folder structure.
* Configure absolute imports.
* Add global fonts (Inter and Space Grotesk).
* Create the global theme.
* Configure dark mode.
* Install Framer Motion, React Query, Zustand, React Hook Form, Zod, and Lucide Icons.

### Deliverables

* Clean project structure.
* Working development server.
* Shared layout.
* Theme provider.
* Global CSS.

