# Development Rules

* Complete one phase before starting the next.
* Do not skip phases.
* Ensure each phase is fully functional and tested.
* Keep code modular and reusable.
* Follow the established design system.
* Maintain consistent coding standards.
* Optimize for performance and accessibility at every stage.
* Document all major decisions and APIs.

# Final Goal

Deliver a production-ready, scalable, visually distinctive streaming platform with a premium user experience, modern architecture, and maintainable codebase suitable for real-world deployment.
